---
// ContactSection コンポーネント
---

<section id="contact" class="section-padding bg-teal-50 dark:bg-teal-950/20">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        お問い合わせ
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground">
        シータ・クリニカル・サポートへのお問い合わせ
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-orange-100 border-l-4 border-orange-500 p-4 rounded-lg mb-6">
        <div class="flex">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-orange-500" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <p class="text-orange-800 font-semibold">
              ⚠️ 研究開始まで1ヶ月を切っている場合は、お急ぎください
            </p>
            <p class="text-orange-700 text-sm mt-1">
              緊急対応チームが迅速にサポートいたします
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
        <form 
          class="space-y-6"
          name="contact"
          method="POST"
          data-netlify="true"
          data-netlify-honeypot="bot-field"
        >
          <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact" />
          <div class="hidden">
            <label>
              Don't fill this out if you're human: <input name="bot-field" />
            </label>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">
              お名前
            </label>
            <input 
              type="text" 
              name="name"
              class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500"
              required
            />
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">
              メールアドレス
            </label>
            <input 
              type="email" 
              name="email"
              class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500"
              required
            />
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">
              研究内容・ご相談内容
            </label>
            <textarea 
              rows="4"
              name="message"
              class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500"
              required
            ></textarea>
          </div>
          
          <button 
            type="submit"
            class="w-full bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white py-4 px-6 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-0.5"
          >
            お問い合わせを送信する
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>